Class DummyEdge

  • java.lang.Object
    • gov.nih.nlm.ling.graph.DummyEdge
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Edge
    public class DummyEdge
extends java.lang.Object
implements Edge
    Represents a dummy edge, which is not derived from a SynDependency. A dummy edge can be used to represent relations between sentences, etc.
    Author:
    Halil Kilicoglu
